title: LG OLED Flex Interview w/ Frank Lee | IFA 2022

media:group.media:title: LG OLED Flex Interview w/ Frank Lee | IFA 2022
media:group.media:description:
LG have exhibited the new LG OLED Flex at IFA 2022. We got the opportunity to interview Frank Lee, the man behind the product strategy of the LG OLED Flex, who gave us insight into the product and what it can do for gaming.
